        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks GB for his help on naturalised plants; comments on spreading of plants.</p> 
<p>Wants to quote GB on the names of species and varieties of <hi rend="italic">Silene</hi> on which C. F. von Gärtner experimented.</p>  
<p>Thinks GB will be disappointed in his book [<hi rend="italic">Natural selection</hi>]. "It will be grievously too hypothetical."</p> 
        </abstract>
